Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:39.61,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Fight the utmost with the stillness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.87,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,무예! 이도류 무사시
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:45.87,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,Martial Arts! Dual Blade Musashi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:51.13,SongOP,ko,0,0,0,,미간이 반짝였다 무사시!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:51.13,SongOP,en,0,0,0,,His eyes shined! Musashi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:06.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구국 제일의 무예가를 꿈꾸는 무사시는 무수한 무예가와 검을 주고받고 있었지만
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.83,0:02:06.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dreaming for the number one Martial Artist of Jipangu State, Musashi was fighting against numberless Martial Artists,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:14.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,상대를 잘못 만났다. 지금은 전국에서 많은 회원을 가진 악명 높은 요시오카 도장의 보스,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.83,0:02:14.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,but he met a wrong opponent. Denshichiro, the boss of Yoshika Dōjō with the most members in the country,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,덴시치로를 적으로 맞이하고야 말았다.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:17.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,is now his opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,ko,0,0,60,,명검 장인, 폭풍을 부르오
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,en,0,0,200,,Master of Sword Maker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.15,0:02:23.16,TitleEP,en,0,0,60,,Calls for a Storm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:40.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 목도로 승부를 보다니 가소롭기 짝이 없구나! 무예가의 승부라는 것은 이런 진검을 써서 하는 것이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:40.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,That's very absurd, to have a match with that wooden sword! A match of Martial Artists will only involve real swords like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,당했소! 나, 죽겠소! 누가 살려주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:55.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,I lost! I'm going to die-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Someone help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,얘야. 뭘 자면서 그러니.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:03:00.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kid, you're half asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 감이었소...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.75,0:03:05.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,It was a persimmon-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아까 감나무 아래 지나가는 중에 떨어졌나 보구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,We were going under a persimmon tree moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 꿈을 꾸고 있었는지는 모르겠지만 크게 흥분하고 있었구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know what were you dreaming about, but you were agitating seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 나도 칼을 원하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn, I want a sword too-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:25.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼을 손에 넣어 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 되겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.62,0:03:25.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will get a sword and become the number one Martial Artist of Jipangu-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이! 이제 곧 사카이 마을이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.71,0:03:29.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,We're soon at Sakai village.
