Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,녀석은 틀림없이 이 사카이 마을에 있을 터이다. 알겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.74,0:03:59.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,He must be in this Sakai village. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:05.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,샅샅이 뒤져서라도 녀석을 찾아내어 발견하면 바로 이 나에게 알려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:05.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Search for him thoroghly and report to me right away as soon as you find out where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애송이라 생각될 테지만 방심하면 큰일난다!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:08.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,He is not just a weak brat, so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:09.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승님!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:13.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:14.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔가?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:14.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예의 칼 장인이 오셨습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sword craftsman you asked for is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋다. 지금 가겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good. Let's go right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:32.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 인물, 켄모치 코테츠야말로, 지팡구국의 기나긴 전국 시대의 역사적으로 유명한 칼 장인이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:32.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,This person, Kenmochi Kotetsu, is a historically famous sword craftsman of a long period of Sengoku era of Jipangu State.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.37,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz26\fs32\fad(0,300)\pos(337,242)\c&H8989FF&}코테츠 작
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:34.37,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an8\frz26\fs32\fad(0,300)\pos(337,242)\c&H8989FF&}Made by Kotetsu
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:40.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그가 만든 칼은 코테츠라 불리며, 검의 길을 끝까지 걸은 자만이 손에 넣을 수 있다고 불려진다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:40.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword crafted by him is called Kotetsu, and it is told that only masters of swords can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:51.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나는 요시오카 도장의 대리 사범, 요시오카 덴시치로라고 하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:51.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am Yoshioka Denshichiro, a substitute instructor of Yoshioka Dōjō.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,켄모치 코테츠이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:53.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kenmochi Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,본론부터 말하자면, 내게 명도 코테츠를 만들어 주셨으면 한다.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,Long story short, I'd like to ask you to make a Kotetsu, an excellent sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거절하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,I reject.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라?! 이 요시오카 도장의 대리 사범의 요청을 거절한다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,What?! You dare to reject the request from the substitute instructor of Yoshioka Dōjō?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너, 설마 지팡구국에 이름을 떨치는 요시오카 덴시치로 님을 모르는 것이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:14.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't you know Yoshioka Denshichiro, a name famous all over Jipangu State?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이름은 안다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:15.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:22.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 어째서 거절하나? 칼을 만드는 게 그렇게 체면 구기는 일은 아니지 않소이까.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.93,0:05:22.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then why do you reject? Crafting a sword isn't something dishonorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안됐지만 이미 칼 만드는 것은 그만두었소.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:25.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,I regret to say that I already gave up crafting swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,관두었다?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:27.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Gave up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떤가. 돈이라면 얼마라도 주겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.02,0:05:31.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,How's this? We'll pay as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 돈 따위를 원하는 것이 아니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do not want money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 무엇을 바라는가?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:36.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아무것도.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.38,0:05:38.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,욕심 없는 녀석이군. 그러나 잘 기억해 두어라.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see that you are without greed. But know this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:46.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네게 어떤 사정이 있던간, 이 내게 칼을 하나 만들어 바쳐야 할 것이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:46.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,Whatever reason you have, you will make and give me a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,실례하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잠깐! 아직 이야기가 끝나지 않았다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.76,0:05:51.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait! He is not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기한은 10일간!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.34,0:05:52.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will allow you ten days!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 내가 직접 가지러 가겠다. 알겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:56.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will go receive it myself. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,괜찮습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you alright with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 지팡구가 넓을 망정 일찍이 내 부탁을 거절한 자는 없었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:07.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,No matter how wide Jipangu is, nobody dared to deny my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,더욱, 거절한 것으로 생명을 잃은 자는 수를 셀 수가 없군.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:13.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Moreover, I can't count how many people lost their lives by denying my request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나... 배가 고파서 힘드오...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:24.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am so tired because I'm so hungry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이, 이건 단고의 향이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,This smell must be {\i1}dango{\i0}-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
