Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,우와! 하늘의 도움이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wow! It's a help from heaven-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,모두! 타셨습니까?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Are you ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.95,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.95,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:08.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋아, 바로 일해 볼까? 일은 간단해.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:08.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Let's get into work right away. Your job is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,주문이 들어오면 가져다 주기만 하면 돼.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.05,0:07:11.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bring these whenever there is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 식사는 몇시이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:13.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,When is the mealtime-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일하고 나서 식사다.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,After you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,3번 테이블 단고 한 접시!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,One {\i1}dango{\i0} plate on the 3th table!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네! 단고 한 접시!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Got it! One {\i1}dango{\i0} plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이, 어이, 빨리 가져다 줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:23.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Hurry up and bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네, 네, 네!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 이곳이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here it is-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리셨소!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.06,0:07:32.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here is your order-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라? 오츠루 씨!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:34.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh? Otsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐에요?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:36.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 오츠루 씨인 것이오! 나이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're Otsuru-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! It's me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,전 당신이 누군지 몰라요.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.34,0:07:41.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:46.20,Default,ko,0,0,0,,에이, 장난은 관두고 나이오, 나! 미야모토 마을의 무사시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:46.20,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't joke on me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I am Musashi, from Miyamoto village-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시라니 몰라요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:48.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't know anyone named Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:49.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.78,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨, 나에요, 나!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:52.78,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.50,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 소리에요! 내 이름은 오타마에요!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:56.50,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?! My name is Otama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨도 참 화나면 귀엽소...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.79,0:08:00.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru, you're cute when you're angry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:06.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭔 짓이야! 아무나! 이 사람 치한이에요!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:06.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Help me! A pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.43,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아니오! 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:09.43,Default,en,0,0,0,,No, that's not it! There's a misunderstanding-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.44,Note,ko,0,0,0,,(PTA: 학부모회)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.44,Note,en,0,0,0,,(PTA: Parent-Teacher Association)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.44,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이러면 곤란해. 그러지 않아도 최근 PTA가 시끄럽게 구는데.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:16.44,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was embarassing. PTA is already annoying us and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.53,Default,ko,0,0,0,,죄송하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.53,Default,en,0,0,0,,I'm sorry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:23.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네게 식당 앞 일은 어울리지 않는 것 같으니 저기서 단고 막대기라도 깎아라.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.53,0:08:23.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,It seems that you're not suited for working in the front of house, so maybe you're better off with carving {\i1}dango{\i0} sticks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.34,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 식사는...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:25.34,Default,en,0,0,0,,Uh, the meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-아직아직!\N-네...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.34,0:08:27.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Not yet!\N-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 찻집 안에서 무사시가 일하고 있습니다.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is working in this tea house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.13,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 놈, 오늘로써 결판을 내 주겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:42.13,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, you're going down as of today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알겠나? 절대 무사시를 놓치면 안 된다!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:45.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Understand? Do not let Musashi run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:46.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:53.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오? 네게도 하나 잘 하는 것이 있구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:53.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Oh, at least you have a specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.17,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 어디 있나!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.17,Default,en,0,0,0,,Where is Musashi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어? 저 목소리는...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:03.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐냐, 뭔 짓이냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비켜라! 무사시가 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Move away! Musashi is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:15.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 저깄다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:29.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,There's Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈춰라!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.39,0:09:39.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시가 저 지붕에서 달아난다!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is running away on that roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장, 끈적지오!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,They're persistent-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:09:59.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어라?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.38,0:09:59.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 각오해라.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:12.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:21.88,Default,ko,0,0,0,,젠장! 자, 하려면 하시오! 겨우 하나 대 여럿이라니 비겁하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:21.88,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dammit! Do as you want-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! One vs many is cowardly-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.09,Default,ko,0,0,0,,비겁이라고 말하면 안 된다. 너 따위는 나 혼자서도 충분하다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.09,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not call this cowardly. I am more than enough to finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨! 먼저 다음 세계로 가겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru! I'm going to the next world earlier than you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.18,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시 놈! 쫒아라! 쫒아!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:40.18,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn that Musashi! Follow him! Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무슨 일이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:43.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's going on-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자! 이 틈이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:46.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Now! Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,와라!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.63,0:10:47.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살았소...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a relief-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이름이...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:54.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.28,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:56.28,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:00.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예의 모르는 놈. 생명의 은인 이름을 막 부르는 놈이 있는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.58,0:11:00.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,You insolent brat. Who dare to call the name of your lifesaver?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,미안하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.56,0:11:02.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sorry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.46,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고맙소.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:04.46,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.38,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 근데 왜 날 구했소?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:07.38,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bu- but why did you saved me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:15.27,Default,ko,0,0,0,,너같은 꼬맹이 하나를 다 자란 성인 여럿이 둘러싸서 죽일 생각을 하는 요시오카의 짓은 용서할 수 없기 때문이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:15.27,Default,en,0,0,0,,I cannot forgive the adults of Yoshioka's misconduct of trying to kill one young brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 얘가 아니오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am not a brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.96,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 넌 뭐냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.96,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 이렇게 보여도 무예가라오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:22.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am a Martial Artist despite how I look-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥, 웃기지 마라! 자기 칼도 없는 얘가! 수치도 모르는 놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:26.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph, don't make me laugh! You don't even have your own sword! You should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 그건 너무했소!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,Th- that's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.93,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검은 무사의 생명! 검을 가지지 않는 놈을 검사로 인정하지 않겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:34.93,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword is the life of a Martial Artist! I will not accept whoever without a sword as a Martial Artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 칼은 명도 관손육(関孫六). 통칭 모노호시자오(장대)다.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.54,0:11:41.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,This sword is an excellent sword of Seki Magoroku. I call it Monohoshizao(clothesline).
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 알아 두어라!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:44.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Never forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.58,Default,ko,0,0,0,,흥. 바보 놈.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.53,0:11:55.58,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hmph. Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.97,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐시라?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.95,0:11:57.97,Default,en,0,0,0,,What did you say-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멋진 척 하지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:02.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't act cool-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.49,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살았소...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:10.49,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was danger-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로 놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:13.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Damn that Kojirō!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:20.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코지로에게 놀림받은 무사시. 칼을 손에 넣을 수 있을 것인가? 질풍노도의 후반을 기다려라!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:20.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi was insulted by Kojirō. Will he ever be able to get a sword? Wait for the stormy latter half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:25.59,Eyecatch,ko,0,0,0,,카라쿠리 검호전 무사시 로드
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:25.59,Eyecatch,en,0,0,0,,Karakuri Kengouden: Musashi Road!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잡았소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Caught one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배고프오...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:43.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hungry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 무사시 씨. 제가 만든 주먹밥이에요. 많이 드세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:53.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here, Musashi. I made these rice balls for you. Eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고맙소, 오츠루 씨. 잘 먹겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you for all of these-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, Otsuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨, 이거 딱딱하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru, these are hard-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.67,Default,ko,0,0,0,,딱딱하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.27,0:13:08.67,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,오츠루 씨...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.34,0:13:10.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Otsuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,먹을 수가 없소.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,I can't eat-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.42,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형! 형!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:14.42,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey there! Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.19,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형 왜 돌을 갉아?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.19,Default,en,0,0,0,,Brother, why are you gnawing stones?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.16,Default,ko,0,0,0,,배, 배가 고파서 못 움직이겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:24.16,Default,en,0,0,0,,I... I am too hungry to move-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.68,Default,ko,0,0,0,,자, 형! 이거 먹어!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:26.68,Default,en,0,0,0,,Here, brother! You can eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 잘 먹었소! 배가 부르오.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was good! I am full-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,얘야, 고맙소. 형 제정신을 되찾았소!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.70,0:13:44.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, kid, I got a grip of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도... 혹시 집으로 가져갈 물고기 아니었소?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:50.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,But... weren't you going to take that fishes to your home-{\i1}dasu{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,괜찮아! 또 잡으면 되니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:53.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,It's all right! I just have to catch them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,좋아! 그럼 형이 잡아주오!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,All right! If that's the case, brother will catch for you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,해냈소!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.30,0:14:04.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.05,Default,ko,0,0,0,,형 대단해!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.05,Default,en,0,0,0,,You're awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,고마워!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.05,0:14:10.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아무것도 아니오.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:12.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,That was nothing-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.12,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도 그 작살은 좋은 잘 듣는 칼인데... 누가 만들었소?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:17.12,Default,en,0,0,0,,But still, that harpoon is a well cutting one... Who made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이건 아빠가 만들었어!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,My dad made this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.73,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아빠?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.73,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.75,Default,ko,0,0,0,,지팡구 제일의 칼 장인, 켄모치 코테츠라고 해!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.27,0:14:24.75,Default,en,0,0,0,,The number one sword craftsman of Jipangu, Kenmochi Kotetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.89,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 그 자식 코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:26.89,Default,en,0,0,0,,I am his son, Kotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait for me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안된다, 안 돼!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:31.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,Nope, no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그런 말 하지 마시고 어떻게든 부탁드리오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't say that, and please help-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.07,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 어떻게든 명인의 칼을 원하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:38.07,Default,en,0,0,0,,I really want a sword of a master craftsman-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 칼 장인은 관뒀다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,I gave up being one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.56,Default,ko,0,0,0,,딱 하나만, 어떻게든, 절 지팡구 제일의 무예가가 되게 해 주시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:46.56,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please, just one for me! Help me become the number one Martial Artist of Jipangu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:52.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나 지팡구 제일이 되는 건 네 노력이다. 내가 그렇게 해주는 게 아니라!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:52.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,You know, your effort will let you become the number one in Jipangu. I don't make you become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:58.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,알고 있소! 저, 지금부터 목숨을 걸고 노력하겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:58.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,I already know-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! From now on, I'll risk my life for that-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그래도... 그래도...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.76,0:15:00.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,But... still...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.77,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나... 어떻게든 명인의 칼을 원하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:03.77,Default,en,0,0,0,,I... really want a sword of a master craftsman-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.70,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 명인의 칼을 갖고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:15.70,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want a sword of an expert-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,원하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want one-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,곤란한 놈이군.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a disturbing brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼 갖고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.51,0:15:23.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,I want a sword-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.02,Default,ko,0,0,0,,칼...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.02,Default,en,0,0,0,,Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:30.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시는 한번 정하면 끈덕졌다.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:30.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Once decided, Musashi was persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:35.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 어떻게든 칼을 원하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:35.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want a sword no matter whatever it takes-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 명인의 칼이 갖고 싶소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:39.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I want a sword of an expert-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.08,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떻게든 부탁드리오! 돈도 드리겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.80,0:15:43.08,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please help me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I'll pay you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-아빠...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,부탁드리오! 나, 지팡구 제일의 무예가로...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:47.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Please-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I need to be the number one Martial Artist of Jipangu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴 스승님... 분하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:03.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Bokuden... I am so mortified-{\i1}dasu{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:05.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bokuden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.82,Default,ko,0,0,0,,나, 이제 지팡구 제일이 되지 못하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:08.82,Default,en,0,0,0,,I won't be able to become the number one anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어이! 무사시! 일어나라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:10.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,Hey! Musashi! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.39,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아! 좋은 아침이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.39,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ah! Good morning-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여기저기 방문한 것 같다만, 네 검의 스승은 누구냐?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,I see you were visiting various places... who is your master of sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제 스승은 츠카하라 보쿠덴이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:24.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,My master is Tsukahara Bokuden-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.59,Default,ko,0,0,0,,거짓말하지 마라! 보쿠덴 님은 제자를 받지 않을 터이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:28.59,Default,en,0,0,0,,Do not lie! Bokuden will not make a pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.29,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그, 근데 나 틀림없이 제자이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:32.29,Default,en,0,0,0,,Bu- but I really am his pupil-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.52,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 보쿠덴 님의 검의 궁극의 목적을 말해 보아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:36.52,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then tell me, the ultimate objective of a sword, according to Master Bokuden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어... 뭐였더라?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:38.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Uh... what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:39.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,왜 그러나?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:39.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.61,0:16:40.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.79,Default,ko,0,0,0,,역시 가짜구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.55,0:16:41.79,Default,en,0,0,0,,You were lying at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,난 거짓말은 하지 않소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,I do not lie-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.00,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그럼 대 보아라!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:46.00,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then tell me right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.65,Default,ko,0,0,0,,안 되겠어, 이 녀석.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:54.65,Default,en,0,0,0,,This guy is a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.90,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아! 잠깐! 기억났소!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:59.90,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wait! Just a moment! I remembered!
Comment: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,剣の究極は戦わずして勝つことなり、武道の武の字はそもそも矛と<みととくほこ>すなわち、武器を止めることなり、老子はよく敵に勝つものは争わず。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:10.23,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검의 궁극은 싸우지 않고 이기는 것. 무도의 무(武) 자는 원래 창(戈)을 막는다(止)는 의미, 즉, 무기를 멈추는 것.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.66,Default,ko,0,0,0,,노자(老子)는 적을 꺾는다는 것은 다투지 않는 것이라 했소.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:05.36,Default,en,0,0,0,,The true meaning of a sword is to win without fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:10.23,Default,en,0,0,0,,Solidness(武) of martial arts(武道) originally mean to stop(止) a spear(戈), in other words, to stop a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.66,Note,en,0,0,0,,(Laozi: 老子. Ancient Chinese philosopher)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.66,Default,en,0,0,0,,According to Laozi, to defeat an emeny is to not fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.71,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:14.71,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,예! 감사하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Yes! Thank you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,애초에 내가 칼 장인를 관둔 것에는 이유가 있다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:22.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,I have a reason to stop being a sword craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.57,Default,ko,0,0,0,,먼저 어떠한 검에도 혼이 깃들어 있음을 알고,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:26.57,Default,en,0,0,0,,First, you must know that a sword has a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,검에는 그것을 만든 자와 쓰는 자의 생각이 담겨,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:31.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,A sword inherits the mind of the craftsman and the user.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 마음이 비뚫어진 자라면 검술과 검이 함께
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:34.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,If one of them has a corrupted mind, then both sword and swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.81,Default,ko,0,0,0,,단지 생명을 빼앗는 도구에 불과하다. 알겠나?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:38.81,Default,en,0,0,0,,becomes nothing more than a device that takes life away. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.24,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘은 모르겠지만 나는 사람을 죽이기 위해 칼을 쓰지 않소.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:44.24,Default,en,0,0,0,,I don't really understand-{\i1}dasu{\i0}, but I don't use swords to kill people-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:48.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 말했다, 무사시. 네 눈이 참 맑구나.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.57,0:17:48.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,Well said, Musashi. Your eyes are clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,잘 자고 난 후니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:50.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Because I had a good sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.86,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시. 잘 들어라. 나는 널 위해 다시 한번만 칼을 만들겠다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.36,0:17:55.86,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, listen to me. I will make swords for you, only once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.76,Default,ko,0,0,0,,저, 정말이오?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.76,Default,en,0,0,0,,Re- really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그러나, 너도 함께 검을 만드는 자의 마음을 배우는 것이 좋다.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:02.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,But you will have to learn the mind of sword craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:02.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,네!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.54,0:18:02.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:13.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,일본도의 재료는 땅 안에 오랫동안 잠자고 있던 순도가 높은 사철이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:13.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,The material of Japanese swords is iron sand of high purity slept for a long time under the grond.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:19.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그 사철을 몇천 회, 몇만 회 마음을 담아 단련시켜 만드는 것이다.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:19.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,The iron sand must be forged thousands times wholeheartedly in order to make one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아직 안 된 걸까나...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:34.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're still not done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-해냈다!\N-해냈구나!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,-We did it!\N-We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.61,Default,ko,0,0,0,,참 잘 했다!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:43.61,Default,en,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 이것이 내가 이 세상에서 만든 마지막 검일 테다. 마음을 담아 써라.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.01,0:18:49.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi, these will be the last swords that I make in this world. Use them to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,ko,0,0,0,,정말 감사하오.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.14,Default,en,0,0,0,,Thank you so much-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:03.64,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코테츠 님! 어라? 나도 갑자기 피곤해졌...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:03.64,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Kotetsu! Huh? I suddenly got sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.22,Default,ko,0,0,0,,여보! 큰일입니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:16.22,Default,en,0,0,0,,Dear! Big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무, 무슨 일인가?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.53,0:19:19.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Wha- what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.41,Default,ko,0,0,0,,요시오카 도장의 사람들이 와서...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:22.41,Default,en,0,0,0,,People from Yoshioka Dōjō came and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.51,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐라? 내가 부탁한 칼을 만들지 않겠다고?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:27.51,Default,en,0,0,0,,What? He didn't made the sword I asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.54,Default,ko,0,0,0,,어떤 분의 의뢰라도 들을 수 없습니다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:31.54,Default,en,0,0,0,,We will not accept any request from anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.11,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그렇다면 어떻게든 만들게 하겠다!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.11,Default,en,0,0,0,,Then I'll make him make one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.30,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-어이!\N-예!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.49,0:19:35.30,Default,en,0,0,0,,-You know what to do!\N-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭘 하시는 것입니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:40.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살려줘! 엄마!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 아이는 코테츠의 검과 교환하겠다. 그렇게 전해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:48.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,I will exchange this kid for a sword made by Kotetsu. Tell him so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.62,Default,ko,0,0,0,,살려줘!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.62,Default,en,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.26,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.26,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:06.37,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 무슨 비열한 패거리오. 코타로는 이 목숨과 교환해서라도 구해내겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:06.37,Default,en,0,0,0,,What a cowardly gang. I will save Kotaro even if I have to exchange my life for him-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.31,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코타로! 기다리시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.31,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kotaro! I'm going to save you-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:17.61,NoteOnAnimeVert,ko,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs64\frz-89.7\frx2\fax0.1\move(558,372,558,372)}(주) 요시오카 도장
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:17.61,NoteOnAnimeVert,ko,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs36\frz-89.7\frx2\fax0.1\move(512,168,512,168)}사카이 지점
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:17.61,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an6\fs64\frz-89.7\frx2\fax0.1\move(558,372,558,372)}Yoshioka Dōjō Inc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:17.61,NoteOnAnime,en,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs36\frz-89.7\frx2\fax0.1\move(512,168,512,168)}Sakai Branch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.55,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시가 있다!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.55,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.40,Default,ko,0,0,0,,-무사시가!\N-네이놈!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:21.40,Default,en,0,0,0,,-Musashi!\N-How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.69,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 등장이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.69,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi is here-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,걱정할 필요는 없소! 칼등이오!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,No need to worry-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! Back side-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.80,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시, 각오해라!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.80,Default,en,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself, Musashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.91,Default,ko,0,0,0,,뭐냐, 저 자세는!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.38,0:20:51.91,Default,en,0,0,0,,What is that pose?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 내가 눈에 들어오지 않는가!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Don't you see me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.87,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코, 코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:00.87,Default,en,0,0,0,,Ko- Kotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.21,Default,ko,0,0,0,,쓸데없는 저항은 관둬라! 그렇지 않으면 이 얘의 목숨은 없다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.21,Default,en,0,0,0,,Give up with your futile resistance! Or this kid will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.03,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 칼을 내려둬라!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.03,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Put down your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.74,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 아빠!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:15.74,Default,en,0,0,0,,D- dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.45,Default,ko,0,0,0,,코타로!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:16.45,Default,en,0,0,0,,Kotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.94,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용서할 수 없소, 덴시치로!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:18.94,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable, Densichiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:31.04,Default,ko,0,0,0,,사, 살려줘. 돈이라면 얼마라도 주겠어!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.86,0:21:31.04,Default,en,0,0,0,,Save me. I'll give you money as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.06,Default,ko,0,0,0,,용서할 수 없소! 넌 지옥으로 보내주겠소!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.06,Default,en,0,0,0,,Unforgivable-{\i1}dasu{\i0}! I will send you to hell-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.98,Default,ko,0,0,0,,무사시! 관두지 못할까!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.57,0:21:41.98,Default,en,0,0,0,,Musashi! Stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.63,Default,ko,0,0,0,,멈추지 마시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:43.63,Default,en,0,0,0,,Don't stop me-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.84,Default,ko,0,0,0,,벌써 잊었냐, 무사시! 검은 위해를 가하기 위해 쓰이는 것이 아니라고!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.84,Default,en,0,0,0,,Did you forget already, Musashi?! A sword may not be used to injure a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.15,Default,ko,0,0,0,,보쿠덴 님도 그렇게 말했을 테다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:50.15,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master Bokuden would said so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.35,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이 놈을 죽이면 검이 더럽혀질 뿐이다!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.41,0:21:55.35,Default,en,0,0,0,,If you kill this guy, you just end up disgracing your sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.85,Default,ko,0,0,0,,아, 알겠소.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.68,0:21:58.85,Default,en,0,0,0,,Alright-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:18.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,이렇게 무사시는 명도 코테츠를 손에 넣었다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.10,0:22:18.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,And this is how Musashi has managed to get an excellent sword, Kotetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:23.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,그리고 또 그 날, 그 유명한 이도류가 탄생한 것이었지만,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:23.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,And also, in that day, that famous dual blade has born,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:28.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}무사시는 아직 깨닫지 못하였다.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:28.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1200)}but Musashi is yet to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:44.34,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,허공의 주머니에 달이
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:44.34,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Sometimes the moon jumps over
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.59,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,뛰어넘어가는 일도 있어
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.05,0:22:47.59,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,the pocket of the empty sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.97,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,큰 소리로 웃으면
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.97,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Laugh loudly and
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.59,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,내일에는 아침이 와
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:52.59,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,a morning will come tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:57.93,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,잃는 것 따위는 아무것도 아니야
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.35,0:22:57.93,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Don't care too much about losing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:01.52,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,계속 해나가! 앞으로 가!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:01.52,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,Keep doing! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.94,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,맨손은 강해
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.94,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,A bare hand is strong
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:14.03,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:14.03,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:22.08,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,인생 그런 거야! 기회가 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:22.08,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how life is! Look, a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:26.80,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,꼬리를 흔들며 쫒아와!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:26.80,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,follows us wagging its tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:37.72,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,그런 거야! 가볍게 가자
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.21,0:23:37.72,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how it is! Let's go lightly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:46.19,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,미래도 그런 거야! 내일이 어라,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:46.19,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,That's how future also is! Look, tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:52.03,SongED1,ko,0,0,0,,양손을 벌리고 웃고 있어!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:52.03,SongED1,en,0,0,0,,is opening its hands and smiling at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,스승, 좋은 울림을 가진 단어이오.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.98,0:24:08.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Master. A word with good echo-{\i1}dasu{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:11.10,Default,ko,0,0,0,,결국엔 나도 제자를 가지게 되었소!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:11.10,Default,en,0,0,0,,Finally, I got a pupil-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:17.32,Default,ko,0,0,0,,제자라는 것은 편리하오! 돈 걱정 없이 단고를 먹게 해 주고, 길을 안내해 주고.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.10,0:24:17.32,Default,en,0,0,0,,A pupil is convinient! He lets me eat {\i1}dango{\i0}s without worry, and guides my path.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:20.47,Default,ko,0,0,0,,근데 이 제자라는 자, 나보다 강하오...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:20.47,Default,en,0,0,0,,But this pupil is powerful than me, heh...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.25,Default,ko,0,0,0,,다음 이야기! 나는 스승이오. 훌륭하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.39,0:24:24.25,Default,en,0,0,0,,Next story! I am a Master! Excellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.01,Default,ko,0,0,0,,질풍노도의 활약을 보시오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:27.01,Default,en,0,0,0,,Be sure to check out the next stormy story-{\i1}dasu{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.98,NoteOnAnime,ko,60,0,60,,{\an7}다음 이야기
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.98,TitleEP,ko,0,0,70,,나는 스승이오\N훌륭하오!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.98,NoteOnAnime,ko,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}기대하세요!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.98,NoteOnAnime,en,60,0,60,,{\an7}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.98,TitleEP,en,0,0,80,,I am a Master\NExcellent!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.98,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!
